{"tid":1805882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"因應駐伊拉克大使館襲擊　美軍增派逾700士兵到中東","createTime":"2020-01-01T02:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T07:52:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a7426814f866be59a1308232862efd2183da32","tid":1805882,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1500449_1_L_20200101090959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1500449_1_L_20200101090959.jpg&h=b0270399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前有示威者在美國駐伊拉克大使館外縱火及破壞。（美聯社）<br />\n美國五角大樓宣布，因應駐伊拉克大使館襲擊事件，將即時部署多約750名士兵到中東地區執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n國防部長埃斯珀表示，增兵是因應美國人員與設施面臨的威脅不斷增加，美軍採取適當的預防措施，保護美方在全世界的民眾和利益。<br />\n<br />\n伊拉克首都巴格達有大批民眾闖入美國大使館破壞及縱火，抗議美軍空襲親伊朗的什葉派武裝組織「真主黨旅」據點。美國國務院表示，駐伊拉克大使館內的人員現時安全，暫時未有計劃撤離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500449-20200101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500449-20200101.htm&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=ff3ebbf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500449-20200101.htm&h=bcd39328\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500449-20200101.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f4e38fde261fb7f9959aa8f31fd22e13f4bc3de3","tid":1805882,"uid":343361,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:25:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n順手嚟埋香港啦喂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0653ecd3cd6b94f6412df809fcd07de08961c37c","tid":1805882,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4e38fde261fb7f9959aa8f31fd22e13f4bc3de3","tid":1805882,"uid":343361,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:25:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-